{"tid":2337672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府：界定貧窮線　二人住戶維持月入萬元水平","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T12:34:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cbccdf567321af12f1773b68d42f618f99e4621c","tid":2337672,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"政府發表新一份香港貧窮情況報告，界定何謂貧困的「貧窮線」，除了二人住戶維持在月入1萬元的水平之外，其餘的都有上升，例如一人戶是月入4500元、四人住戶是月入21400元，6人或以上是月入23000元，低於有關水平即屬於貧窮。<br />\n<br />\n在恆常現金政策介入後，貧窮人口由政策介入前的約149萬，減少至近110萬，政策介入後新增的73500名貧窮人口，在職住戶佔三成半，失業住戶佔5.7%，其餘的是非從事經濟活動的住戶。"},{"pid":"6b83acd63d63dc39150924c3403e4e609845145e","tid":2337672,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566830-20201223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566830-20201223.htm&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=968a7b29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566830-20201223.htm&h=e8f6dedd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566830-20201223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9a953ff7bcfde810d1d5552dee91244590cd04d6","tid":2337672,"uid":358604,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SWu2fNH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSWu2fNH.png&h=fb8e126a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}